            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Hd1e108">Rubrica 3</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De conscientia benignitatis et malignitatis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>¶ De conscientia benignitatis
      <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>et malignitatis. ¶ Rubrica. 3
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>Ratius epistolarum li.
      <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>i. e. i. <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e127"/>Hic murus
      <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>eneus extat: Nil conscii sibi: nul
      <lb ed="#V" n="66" break="no"/>la pallescere culpa. 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e134">
               <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e138">¶ Tullius de senectute: Conscientia bene acte
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>vite multorumque beneficiorum recordatio ino
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>cundissima est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e147"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e149"> Idem tuscalanarum que
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>stionum li. 2. Nullum theatrum virtute et
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>conscientia maius est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e157">
               <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e161">¶ Quidius de fastis li. i. Conscientia mens
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>vt cuique sua est sic concipit intra Pectore
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>profecto spemque metumque suo. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e169"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e171"> Lib. 4 Con
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>scia mens recti fame mendacia ridet.
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>Sed nos in vitium credula turba sumus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>Seneca in prouerb. Plerique famam: conscien
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>tiam pauci verentur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e183">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e187">¶ Paulus apostolus epistola. 2. ad corinth. c. i. Slia
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>nostra hoc est testimonium conscient ie nostre.
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>Statius thebandos li. 2. O sper timidum scelus </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e195">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e199">¶ Iuuenalis li. 2. satis i. Cui frigida mens est
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>Criminibus tacita sudant praecordia culpa.
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>Marcialis cocus li. vndique suscepto. c. 6.
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>Ibis ad occultos tramites loca deuia mundi
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>Peccatum tecum est: conscientie culpa comes.
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>Alterius censor: censor et esto tuus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e213">
               <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e217">¶ Ambrosius de officiis li. 2. c. i. Uitam bea
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>tam effciunt tranquillitas conscientie et se
        <lb ed="#V" n="90" break="no"/>curitas innocentie. <!--79.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="26-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e232">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e236">¶ Augustinus in epig. prospe. 8. emp. Bo
        <lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>na conscientia tranquillum facit animu.
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>Macrobius de somno scipionis li. 2. et fi
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>Uirtutis fructum sapiens in conscientia ponit:
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>minus perfctus in gloria. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e248">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e252">¶ Cato. c. 2 Conscius ipse sibi: de se putat
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>omnia dici. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e258">
               <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e262">¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 7. c. 32. Totum vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>tiosum geritur vbi conscientie puritas non ha
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>betur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e270"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e272"> Li. 8. e. 18. Sicut conscientia leta est
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>que prouehitur meritis: ita sub reatu iacet
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>qui se imparem cognoscit muneribus conse
        <lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>cutis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e282"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e284"> Libro. 11. c. 8. Quid acquiri puta
        <lb ed="#V" n="14" break="no"/>tur vbi conscientia bona perditur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e290">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e294">¶ Isidorus soliloquiorum li. 2. c. 3. Deus con
        <lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>scientias iudicat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e301"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e303"> c. 37. Etsi non te damnet
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>publica fama: condennat propria conscia. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e309"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e311"> c. 38
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>Conscientia rei semper tin pena est. Mens
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>male conscientie propriis agitatur stimulis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e319">
               <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e323">¶ Prouerb. vulgar. Lamore guasta la conscia </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
